      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Catnap Ruined",
        "Client": "Cat-Napping Felyne",
        "Description": "All the shade in the Shrine\r\nRuins makes it purr-fect fur\r\nnapping, but two Arzuros are\r\nmaking such a ruckus with\r\ntheir tussling, I can\u0027t catch a\r\nwink! I need you to get back\r\nmy mew-ty sleep, Hunter!",
        "Target": "Hunt 2 Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Une sieste g\u00E2ch\u00E9e",
        "Client": "Felyne herbe \u00E0 chat",
        "Description": "Il y a beaucoup d\u0027ombre au\r\nTemple oubli\u00E9, ce qui en fait\r\nl\u0027endroit id\u00E9al pour une sieste.\r\nMais deux Arzuros font un boucan\r\nd\u0027enfer et m\u0027emp\u00EAchent\r\nde dormir ! J\u0027ai besoin\r\nde dormir, moi !",
        "Target": "Chasser 2 Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Rissa alle Rovine sacre",
        "Client": "Felyne appisolata",
        "Description": "C\u0027\u00E8 tanta ombra alle Rovine\r\nsacre, il che le rende il posto\r\nideale per un pisolino. Ma due\r\nArzuros si azzuffano e fanno\r\nbaccano. Non riesco a riposare!\r\nAiutami a dormire, per favore.",
        "Target": "Caccia 2 Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Ruiniertes Nickerchen",
        "Client": "D\u00F6sende Felyne",
        "Description": "Die Schatten in den Heiligen\r\nRuinen machen den Ort zu\r\neinem schnurrigen Platz f\u00FCr ein\r\nNickerchen, aber zwei Arzuros\r\nmachen so einen Krach, dass ich\r\nkein Auge zudr\u00FCcken kann!\r\nIch brauche deine Hilfe!",
        "Target": "Erjage zwei Arzuros.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Siesta molesta en el templo",
        "Client": "Felyne siestera",
        "Description": "El Templo olvidado es un sitio\r\nmorrongotudo para dormir a la\r\nsombra, pero hay dos Arzuros\r\npele\u00E1ndose y, con tanto ruido,\r\n\u00A1no puedo pegar ojo! Ay\u00FAdame a\r\nconciliar el sue\u00F1o.",
        "Target": "Caza 2 Arzuros",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0417\u0430\u0432\u0430\u0440\u0443\u0448\u043A\u0430 \u0432 \u0420\u0443\u0438\u043D\u0430\u0445 \u0441\u0432\u044F\u0442\u0438\u043B\u0438\u0449\u0430",
